		<note>N. P. Chakracarti, as editor of Sastri's work, commented in a footnote: <q>Reading or the last two sylables in the first line and of the first two in the second is doubtful.</q> <hi rend="check">Ought one to read <foreign>saindhavāvānartha</foreign> and emend this to <foreign>saindhava-dānārthaṁ</foreign>?</hi></note>
                  </app>
	<app loc="B2">
		<lem>kumārabhaṭṭeṇa</lem>
