         <div type="translation">
<p n="A1">The states arisen from a cause, their cause the Tathāgata proclaims, as well as their cessation: This is the teaching of the Great Ascetic.</p>
<p n="B1-B2">In the year 4, on day 10 of the waxing fortinight of Caitra during the reign of Śrī Mahendrapāladeva <supplied reason="subaudible">the image</supplied> was set up by Kumārabhaṭṭa as a gift to the Saindhava <supplied reason="explanation">monks</supplied>.</p>
